20stand%20out%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20smart%20and%20intentional%20about%20managing%20your%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20had%20known%20this%20when%20I%20started%20out%2C%20I%20would've%20gone%20much%20further%2C%20much%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEthan%20Evans%20is%20a%20retired%20Amazon%20vice%20president%20with%20over%2023%20years%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20business%20executive.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-manage-career-get-promoted-from-amazon-vp-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718615101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f915fa961b37edf396d48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-manage-career-get-promoted-from-amazon-vp-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ethan%20Evans%20became%20a%20VP%20at%20Amazon%20in%20eight%20years%2C%20but%20he%20wishes%20he%20would've%20done%20things%20differently.%20He%20teaches%20his%20clients%20these%20seven%20strategies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ethan%20Evans)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-manage-career-get-promoted-from-amazon-vp-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Loco%20Pilot%2C%20Assistant%20Among%203%20Railway%20Staffers%20Killed%20In%20Bengal%20Collision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20railway%20staff%20members%20were%20among%20eight%20people%20killed%20when%20a%20goods%20train%20rear-ended%20the%20Silchar-Sealdah%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20at%208.55%20am%20today%2C%20railway%20officials%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goods%20train%2C%20which%20reportedly%20jumped%20a%20signal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanchanjunga-express-collides-with-goods-train-in-west-bengals-darjeeling-rescue-on-5906662%5C%22%3Ecollided%20with%20the%20passenger%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20same%20track%20around%208.55%20am.%20Three%20coaches%20of%20the%20express%20train%20derailed%2C%20with%20one%20of%20them%20climbing%20onto%20the%20locomotive%20of%20the%20goods%20rake%20because%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20collision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20five%20passengers%20and%20three%20railway%20staffers%20-%20the%20locomotive%20pilot%20and%20assistant%20locomotive%20pilot%20of%20the%20goods%20rake%20and%20the%20guard%20in%20the%20express%20train%20-%20were%20killed%20and%20nearly%2050%20others%20were%20injured.%20Officials%20said%20the%20casualties%20could%20have%20been%20much%20higher%20but%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20last%20two%20coaches%20of%20the%20express%20train%20were%20the%20guard%20coach%20and%20the%20cargo%20van.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20coaches%20of%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20and%20the%20engine%20and%20five%20containers%20of%20the%20goods%20trains%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20collision%2C%20which%20occurred%20near%20Rangapani%20station%2C%20close%20to%20New%20Jalpaiguri.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanchanjungha-express-train-accident-live-updates-kanchanjungha-express-goods-train-collide-in-darjeeling-rescue-ops-on-5906811%5C%22%3Erescue%20operation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20complete.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20passes%20through%20the%20Chicken's%20Neck%2C%20a%20narrow%20corridor%20that%20connects%20the%20Northeast%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20At%20least%2010%20trains%20have%20been%20diverted%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKavach%20Not%20Implemented%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Sabyasachi%20De%2C%20the%20Chief%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20of%20the%20Northeast%20Frontier%20Railway%2C%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20accident%20is%20being%20investigated%20and%20while%20some%20trains%20have%20been%20diverted%2C%20movement%20will%20not%20be%20hampered%20because%20the%20Aluabari-Siliguri-New%20Jalpaiguri%20line%20is%20being%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20Board%20Chairperson%20Jaya%20Varma%20Sinha%20confirmed%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20loco%20pilot%20and%20assistant%20loco%20pilot%20of%20the%20goods%20train%20and%20the%20guard%20of%20the%20express%20train.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injured%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20North%20Bengal%20Medical%20College%20in%20Siliguri.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20get%20them%20the%20best%20possible%20medical%20aid%20so%20that%20their%20lives%20can%20be%20saved%20and%20they%20can%20recover%20as%20fast%20as%20possible...%20The%20unaffected%20portion%20of%20the%20train%20is%20being%20sent%20to%20its%20destination%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20passengers.%20For%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20helpdesks%20and%20helpline%20numbers%20have%20been%20set%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sinha%20said%20an%20inquiry%20will%20be%20conducted%20and%20admitted%20that%20the%20Kavach%20anti-collision%20system%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20on%20the%20route%20used%20by%20the%20train.%20She%20added%2C%20however%2C%20that%20it%20has%20been%20planned%20on%20the%20Delhi-Guwahati%20route.%20When%20implemented%2C%20this%20will%20cover%20at%20least%20some%20sections%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Assam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20the%20much-vaunted%20indigenously%20developed%20Kavach%20system%20was%20also%20talked%20about%20after%20the%20triple%20train%20collision%20in%20Odisha's%20Balasore%20in%20June%20last%20year%2C%20in%20which%20293%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20over%201%2C200%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20System%20Works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%2C%20Hindi%20for%20armour%2C%20is%20an%20anti-collision%20system%20developed%20by%20the%20Research%20Design%20and%20Standards%20Organisation%20(RDSO)%20to%20achieve%20the%20goal%20of%20%26quot%3Bzero%20accidents%26quot%3B.%20The%20technology%20is%20Safety%20Integrity%20Level%204%20(SIL-4)%20certified%20-%20the%20highest%20certification%20level%20-%20meaning%20that%20there%20is%20a%20probability%20of%20just%20one%20error%20by%20Kavach%20in%2010%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20uses%20high-frequency%20radio%20communication%20and%20operates%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20continuous%20update%20of%20movement%20to%20prevent%20collisions.%20If%20it%20senses%20that%20an%20accident%20is%20about%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20automatically%20activates%20the%20brakes%20of%20the%20train%20on%20routes%20where%20the%20system%20is%20implemented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20per%20km%2C%20it%20is%20also%20significantly%20lower%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20such%20technology%20used%20in%20other%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20system%20has%20been%20put%20in%20place%20in%201%2C500%20km%20of%20tracks%20so%20far%20and%203%2C000%20km%20will%20be%20covered%20this%20year.%20The%20length%20of%20India's%20railway%20network%20is%20over%201%20lakh%20km.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelpline%20numbers%20released%20by%20the%20Railways%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20033-23508794%20and%20033-23833326%20(Sealdah)%20and%2003612731621%2C%2003612731622%20and%2003612731623%20at%20Guwahati.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718615100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fs02337lo_bengal-train-accident_625x300_17_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-train-accident-bengal-train-collision-west-bengal-loco-pilot-assistant-among-3-railway-staffers-killed-in-bengal-collision-5907934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20railway%20staff%20members%20were%20among%20eight%20people%20killed%20when%20a%20goods%20train%20rear-ended%20the%20Silchar-Sealdah%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20at%208.55%20am%20toda