mesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fkim-soo-hyun-croons-queen-of-tears-ots-during-a-memorable-performance-in-bangkok-during-2024-asia-tour%2Farticleshow%2F111055900.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111055900.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKim%20Soo%20Hyun%20wows%20fans%20at%20'EYES%20ON%20YOU'%20Asia%20Tour%20in%20Bangkok%20with%20performance%20of%20'Sorry%2C%20Hate%2C%20Love'%20OST%20from%20'Queen%20of%20Tears'.%20Fans%20flood%20social%20media%20with%20love.%20Kim%20Soo%20Hyun%20expresses%20gratitude%20for%20the%20warm%20reception.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zhang%20Yimou%20to%20Direct%20%E2%80%98Three-Body%20Problem%E2%80%99%20Movie%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718613773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThree-Body-Zhang-Yimou-collage-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236039800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zhang%20Yimou%2C%20director%20of%20many%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20most%20spectacular%20and%20successful%20movies%2C%20is%20to%20try%20his%20hand%20at%20sci-fi.%20He%20will%20direct%20a%20film%20adaptation%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Three-Body%20Problem.%E2%80%9D%20The%20project%20was%20announced%20Sunday%20by%20Wang%20Changtian%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Enlight%20Media%2C%20one%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20top%20three%20studios%2C%20at%20a%20forum%20organized%20within%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fzhang-yimou-three-body-problem-film-1236039800%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fzhang-yimou-three-body-problem-film-1236039800%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fzhang-yimou-three-body-problem-film-1236039800%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Kavach%3F%20Safety%20System%20Missing%20On%20Bengal%20Route%20Where%20Trains%20Crashed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKavach%2C%20the%20made-in-India%20system%20to%20help%20prevent%20accidents%20if%20two%20trains%20are%20travelling%20on%20the%20same%20line%2C%20was%20not%20available%20on%20the%20tracks%20in%20Darjeeling%20where%20the%20two%20trains%20collided%20today.%20At%20least%20eight%20passengers%20have%20died%20and%20over%2050%20others%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20goods%20train%20rammed%20the%20Kolkata-bound%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20from%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20explaining%20the%20Kavach%20system%20went%20viral%20following%20today's%20crash%2C%20officials%20said%20the%20system%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20installed%20in%20much%20of%20the%20rail%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20The%20Railways%20plans%20to%20deploy%20the%20safety%20system%20on%20the%20Delhi-Guwahati%20route%20under%20its%20goal%20to%20cover%20over%206%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20by%20next%20year.%20Bengal%20falls%20within%20the%203%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20set%20to%20be%20protected%20by%20Kavach%20this%20year.%20The%20system%20will%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20Delhi-Howrah%20route%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaya%20Varma%20Sinha%2C%20Chairman%20of%20Railway%20Board%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Kavach%20is%20in%20place%20on%20over%201%2C500%20km%20of%20tracks.%20The%20Centre%20had%20planned%20to%20bring%202%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20network%20under%20Kavach%20during%202022-23%20and%20aims%20to%20cover%20around%2034%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20network.%20The%20Indian%20Railway%20system%20is%20over%201%20lakh%20kilometres%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Kavach%20was%20deployed%2C%20something%20like%20this%20accident%20could%20likely%20be%20avoided.%20However%2C%20it's%20a%20costly%20system%20to%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Railway%20Board%20Prempal%20Sharma%20told%20NDTV.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Is%20Kavach%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20is%20an%20automatic%20train%20protection%20(ATP)%20system%2C%20indigenously-developed%20by%20the%20Research%20Design%20and%20Standards%20Organisation%20(RSCO)%20with%20three%20Indian%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20system%20controls%20the%20speeding%20of%20trains%20but%20also%20helps%20locomotive%20drivers%20to%20avoid%20missing%20danger%20signals%20and%20ensure%20that%20trains%20run%20safely%20especially%20in%20low-visibility%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20controls%20train%20speed%20by%20automatically%20braking%20if%20the%20driver%20fails%20to%20apply%20the%20brakes%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERFID%20(Radio%20Frequency%20Identification)%20tags%20are%20placed%20on%20tracks%20and%20at%20station%20yard%20and%20signals%20for%20identifying%20the%20tracks%20and%20locating%20the%20train%20and%20its%20direction.%20When%20the%20system%20is%20activated%2C%20all%20trains%20within%205%20km%20will%20stop%20to%20let%20the%20train%20on%20an%20adjacent%20track%20to%20pass%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Board%20Display%20of%20Signal%20Aspect%20(OBDSA)%20helps%20the%20loco%20pilots%20view%20the%20signals%20even%20when%20the%20visibility%20is%20low%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%20Usually%2C%20loco%20pilots%20have%20to%20look%20out%20of%20the%20window%20to%20spot%20the%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20system%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20a%20loco%20pilot%20when%20approaching%20a%20'red%20signal'%20and%20applies%20automatic%20brakes%20if%20necessary%20to%20prevent%20overshooting%20the%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20he%20had%20personally%20tested%20the%20safety%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRear-end%20collision%20testing%20is%20successful.%20Kavach%20automatically%20stopped%20the%20locomotive%20before%20380%20m%20of%20other%20locomotive%20at%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHere%20is%20a%20video%20of%20the%20Railways%20Minister%20explaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShri%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshwiniVaishnaw%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AshwiniVaishnaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnHon'ble%20Railway%20Minister%20briefs%20during%20live%20testing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fkavach%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23kavach%3C%2Fa%3E%20automatic%20train%20protection%20technology%20in%20Lingampalli%20-%20Vikarabad%20section%2C%20South%20Central%20Railway%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNationalSafetyDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NationalSafetyDay%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRailMinIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RailMinIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrmsecunderabad%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40drmsecunderabad%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjtW5EXECm3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjtW5EXECm3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20South%20Central%20Railway%20(%40SCRailwayIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCRailwayIndia%2Fstatus%2F1499640390672338949%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20system%20also%20relays%20SoS%20messages%20durin