06662%5C%22%3EKanchanjunga%20Express%20accident%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20goods%20train%20that%20hit%20a%20Kolkata-bound%20express%20train%20this%20morning%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Darjeeling%20district%20had%20overshot%20the%20signal%2C%20officials%20said.%20At%20least%20eight%20died%20and%20two%20dozen%20passengers%20suffered%20injuries%20after%20the%20express%20train%20traveling%20from%20Silchar%2C%20Assam%20to%20Sealdah%2C%20Kolkata%20was%20rammed%20by%20the%20goods%20train%20near%20Rangapani%20station%2C%20close%20to%20New%20Jalpaiguri.%20The%20last%20three%20coaches%20of%20the%20express%20train%20were%20derailed%20and%20many%20more%20were%20affected%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loco-pilot%20of%20the%20goods%20train%2C%20his%20assistant%2C%20and%20the%20guard%20of%20the%20passenger%20train%20are%20among%20the%20eight%20victims.%20At%20least%2010%20trains%20have%20been%20diverted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanchanjunga%20Express%20is%20frequently%20used%20by%20tourists%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20popular%20hill%20station%20of%20Darjeeling.%20The%20route%20crosses%20the%20narrow%20strip%20of%20land%20called%20Chicken's%20Corridor%2C%20which%20links%20the%20Northeast%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp0mv8oo8_train-accident_625x300_17_June_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20is%20an%20automatic%20signal%20section%20and%20remains%20extremely%20busy%20with%20parallel%20lines%2C%20which%20means%20there%20are%20higher%20chances%20of%20other%20trains%20being%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20railway%20accident%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20saddening.%20Condolences%20to%20those%20who%20lost%20t