-shameless-producer-indian-woman-freedom-fighter-doc-abbakka-1236039760%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fcannes-shameless-producer-indian-woman-freedom-fighter-doc-abbakka-1236039760%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%2015%20Years%20Behind%20China%20On%20Nuclear%20Power%2C%20Claims%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20as%20many%20as%2015%20years%20behind%20China%20on%20developing%20high-tech%20nuclear%20power%20as%20Beijing's%20state-backed%20technology%20approach%20and%20extensive%20financing%20give%20it%20the%20edge%2C%20a%20report%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%2027%20nuclear%20reactors%20under%20construction%20with%20average%20construction%20timelines%20of%20about%20seven%20years%2C%20far%20faster%20than%20other%20countries%2C%20said%20the%20study%20by%20Information%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Innovation%20Foundation%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20nonpartisan%20research%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20rapid%20deployment%20of%20ever-more%20modern%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20over%20time%20produces%20significant%20scale%20economies%20and%20learning-by-doing%20effects%2C%20and%20this%20suggests%20that%20Chinese%20enterprises%20will%20gain%20an%20advantage%20at%20incremental%20innovation%20in%20this%20sector%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20has%20the%20world's%20largest%20fleet%20of%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20considers%20the%20virtually%20emissions-free%20electricity%20source%20to%20be%20critical%20in%20curbing%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20two%20large%20plants%20in%20Georgia%20came%20online%20in%202023%20and%202024%20billions%20of%20dollars%20over%20budget%20and%20delayed%20by%20years%2C%20no%20U.S.%20nuclear%20reactors%20are%20being%20built.%20A%20high-tech%20plant%20that%20had%20been%20planned%20to%20be%20built%20at%20a%20U.S.%20lab%20was%20canceled%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20state-owned%20banks%20can%20offer%20loans%20as%20low%20as%201.4%25%2C%20far%20lower%20than%20available%20in%20Western%20economies.%20Its%20nuclear%20power%20industry%20has%20benefited%20from%20sustained%20state%20support%20and%20localization%20strategies%20that%20has%20allowed%20China%20to%20dominate%20sectors%20like%20renewable%20power%20and%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20first%20so-called%20fourth-generation%20high-temperature%20gas%20cooled%20reactor%20at%20Shidao%20Bay%20came%20online%20last%20December.%C2%A0The%20China%20Nuclear%20Energy%20Association%20claims%20that%20the%20project%20involved%20the%20development%20of%20more%20than%202%2C200%20sets%20of%20%26quot%3Bworld-first%20equipment%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20total%20localization%20rate%20of%20domestically%20produced%20materials%20of%2093.4%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBackers%20of%20high-tech%20reactors%20say%20they%20are%20safer%20and%20more%20efficient%20than%20current%20plants.%20Critics%20say%20some%20new%20reactors%20introduce%20proliferation%20and%20material%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20not%20all%20been%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20China.%20The%20China%20Nuclear%20Energy%20Association%20has%20warned%20that%20there%20was%20a%C2%A0severe%20glut%20in%20nuclear%20component%20production%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%20competition%26quot%3B%20was%20driving%20down%20prices%20and%20causing%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStephen%20Ezell%2C%20the%20report's%20author%2C%20said%20if%20the%20U.S.%20is%20serious%20about%20nuclear%20it%20should%20develop%20a%20robust%20national%20strategy%20involving%20more%20investment%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20identifying%20and%20accelerating%20promising%20technologies%2C%20and%20supporting%20development%20of%20a%20skilled%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20America%20is%20behind%2C%20it%20can%20certainly%20catch%20up%20technologically%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ezell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20Energy%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718607480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F4fjev0ag_biden-xi-afp_625x300_29_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-15-years-behind-china-on-nuclear-power-claims-report-5906527%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20is%20as%20many%20as%2015%20years%20behind%20China%20on%20developing%20high-tech%20nuclear%20power%20as%20Beijing's%20state-backed%20technology%20approach%20and%20extensive%20financing%20give%20it%20the%20edge%2C%20a%20report%20said%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-15-years-behind-china-on-nuclear-power-claims-report-5906527%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-15-years-behind-china-on-nuclear-power-claims-report-5906527%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-15-years-behind-china-on-nuclear-power-claims-report-5906527%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20weather%3A%20Extreme%20heat%20in%20Southwest%20and%20Midwest%2C%20Rockies%20see%20snow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718607271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111054326%2Cimgsize-1053760.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-weather-turmoil-extreme-heat-in-southwest-and-midwest-rockies-see-snow%2Farticleshow%2F111053137.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fwor