%20deleted%20the%20evidence%20from%20his%20iPhone.%20However%2C%20the%20messages%20were%20still%20accessible%20on%20the%20iMac%20due%20to%20the%20synchronisation%20of%20the%20family's%20devices%20with%20the%20same%20Apple%20ID.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20Apple%20did%20not%20inform%20users%20that%20deleting%20a%20message%20on%20one%20device%20does%20not%20remove%20it%20from%20all%20linked%20devices.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20told%20a%20message%20is%20deleted%2C%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%20believe%20it's%20deleted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man's%20wife%20found%20the%20messages%20and%20filed%20for%20a%20divorce%2C%20a%20move%20that%20has%20cost%20him%20over%205%20million%20pounds%2C%20said%20The%20Times.%20He%20described%20the%20divorce%20as%20%26quot%3Bpainful%20and%20raw%2C%26quot%3B%20stating%20that%20a%20more%20rational%20conversation%20could%20have%20saved%20his%20marriage%20if%20the%20messages%20hadn't%20been%20discovered%20so%20brutally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20been%20able%20to%20talk%20to%20her%20rationally%20and%20she%20had%20not%20had%20such%20a%20brutal%20realisation%20of%20it%2C%20I%20might%20still%20be%20married%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20brutal%20way%20of%20finding%20out%20%5Bfor%20my%20wife%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20is%20now%20suing%20Apple%20for%205%20million%20pounds%20and%20is%20seeking%20to%20turn%20his%20lawsuit%20into%20a%20class-action%20suit%20for%20others%20who%20might%20have%20faced%20similar%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20from%20Apple%20about%20how%20message%20deletion%20works%20led%20to%20this%20situation.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20it's%20all%20because%20Apple%20told%20me%20my%20messages%20were%20deleted%20when%20they%20weren't.%20If%20the%20message%20had%20said%2C%20'These%20messages%20are%20deleted%20on%20this%20device'%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20clue%2C%20or%20'These%20messages%20are%20deleted%20on%20this%20device%20only'%20that%20would%20have%20been%20even%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHis%20lawyer%2C%20Simon%20Walton%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2F06%2F13%2Fcheating-husband-sues-apple-sex-messages%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CApple%20had%20not%20been%20clear%20with%20users%20as%20to%20what%20happens%20to%20messages%20they%20send%20and%20receive%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20delete.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Walton%20said%20that%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20iPhone%20informs%20the%20user%20that%20%26quot%3Bmessages%20have%20been%20deleted%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20claims%20wasn't%20true%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20because%20they%20are%20still%20found%20on%20other%20linked%20devices%20-%20something%20Apple%20doesn't%20tell%20its%20users.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Beager%20to%20hear%20from%20other%20Apple%20customers%20who%20have%20experienced%20similar%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718606100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Fs59joum8_apple-generic-reuters-650_625x300_30_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-sues-apple-after-wife-discovers-deleted-messages-with-sex-worker-5906701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20UK%20businessman%20is%20suing%20Apple%20after%20his%20wife%20found%20out%20his%20%26quot%3Bdeleted%26quot%3B%20messages%20to%20sex%20workers%20on%20their%20family%20iMac.%20The%20messages%2C%20which%20he%20believed%20were%20%26quot%3Bdeleted%20permanently%26quot%3B%20from%20his%20iPhone%2C%20led%20to%20his%20wife%20filing%20for%20divorce%2C%20reported%20The%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-sues-apple-after-wife-discovers-deleted-messages-with-sex-worker-5906701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-sues-apple-after-wife-discovers-deleted-messages-with-sex-worker-5906701%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-sues-apple-after-wife-discovers-deleted-messages-with-sex-worker-5906701%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Masaba's%20special%20post%20for%20Satyadeep%20Misra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718606091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111052486%2Cimgsize-20718.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmasaba-gupta-wishes-to-be-a-father-satyadeep-misra-on-fathers-day-with-a-special-post%2Farticleshow%2F111052486.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111052486.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFather%E2%80%99s%20Day%20was%20observed%20on%20June%2016%2C%202024%2C%20and%20several%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20have%20also%20shared%20special%20messages%20and%20throwback%20pictures%20to%20mark%20the%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmasaba-gupta-wishes-to-be-a-father-satyadeep-misra-on-fathers-day-with-a-special-post%2Farticleshow%2F111052486.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Team%20Thackeray%20vs%20Shinde%20Sena%20Amid%20EVM%20Row%20On%20Seat%20INDIA%20Lost%20By%2048%20Votes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20news%20reports%20claiming%20that%20the%20phone%20of%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20candidate's%20aide%20was%20connected%20to%20an%20EVM%20during%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20Mumbai's%20North%20West%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20leaders%20of%20NDA%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20trading%20barbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Waikar%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20West%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20just%2048%20votes.%20The%20runner-up%20was%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray).%20The%20Thackery-led%20faction%20bagged%20nine%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20while%20Mr%20Shinde's%20Sena%20got%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20news%20reports%20emerged%2C%20leaders%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%20demanded%20that%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20counting%20day%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20trashed%20the%20news%20reports%20and%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20publishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVandana%20Suryavanshi%2C%20returning%20officer%20of%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20said%20an%20EVM%20was%20a%20standalone%20system%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20an%20OTP%20to%20unlock%20it.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20programmable%20and%20has%20no%20wireless%20communication%20capabilities.%20It%20is%20a%20lie%20being%20spread%20by%20a%20newspaper%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20official%2C%20however%2C%20admitted%20that%20the%20personal%20mobile%20phone%20of%20one%20Dinesh%20Gurav%2C%20data%20entry%20operator%20of%20Jogeshwari%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20was%20found%20with%20an%20unauthorised%20person%20--%20Mr%20Waikar's%20brother-in-law%20Mangesh%20Pandilkar%20--%20and%20action%20is%20being%20taken.%20%26quot%3BData%20entry%20and%20vote%20counting%20are%20two%20different%20aspects.%20An%20OTP%20enables%20the%20ARO%20to%20open%20the%20encore%20login%20system%20for%20data%20entry.%20The%20counting%20process%20is%20independent%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20mobile%20phone%2C%20which%20is%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20and%20is%20being%20probed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20neither%20Mr%20Waikar%20nor%20Mr%20Kirtikar%20had%20sought%20a%20recount%20of%20votes.%20She%20added%20that%20CCTV%20footage%20cannot%20be%20given%20without%20court%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20son%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%2C%20said%20the%20Election%20Commission%20lacks%20the%20courage%20to%20release%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20counting%20centre.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20had%20suspicions%20about%20this%20regime%20tampering%20with%20EVMs.%20Even%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20expressed%20his%20views%2C%20claiming%20everything%20can%20be%20hacked.%20Despite%20several%20requests%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20does%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20release%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20counting%20day%20that%20would%20support%20our%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20Thackeray%20also%20got%20support%20from%20its%20ally%20Congress.%20Senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20said%20the%20poll%20result%20of%20Mumbai%20North%20West%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20must%20be%20stayed.%20The%20Election%20Commission%2C%20he%20said%2C%20must%20call%20a%20meeting%20of%20all%20parties%20and%20discuss%20this%20issue%20thoroughly.%20%26quot%3BThere%20must%20be%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20unauthorised%20used%20of%20the%20mobile%20phone.%20The%20FIR%20report%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20row%20over%20the%20news%20reports%20on%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20West%20seat%20was%20fuelled%20by%20a%20social%20media%20remark%20by%20X%20boss%20and%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk.%20Responding%20to%20a%20post%20on%20Puerto%20Rico%20elections%2C%20Musk%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20eliminate%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20The%20risk%20of%20being%20hacked%20by%20humans%20or%20AI%2C%20while%20small%2C%20is%20still%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20drew%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar.%20Saying%20that%20while%20Musk's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20other%20places%20where%20voting%20machines%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20Internet%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%20EVMs%20in%20India%20are%20secure%20and%20isolated%20from%20any%20network%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20way%20in%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20latched%20on%20to%20Elon%20Musk's%20remark%20to%20question%20the%20EVM%20method.%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20EVMs%20in%20India%20%26quot%3Bare%20a%20'black%20box'%20and%20nobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20scrutinize%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSerious%20concerns%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20transparency%20in%20our%20electoral%20process.%20Democracy%20ends%20up%20becoming%20a%20sham%20and%20prone%20to%20fraud%20when%20institutions%20lack%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20sharing%20Musk's%20post%20and%20a%20news%20report%20on%20Ravindra%20Waitkar's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20and%20a%20Congress%20ally%2C%20shared%20Musk's%20post%20with%20a%20note%3A%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20is%20to%20remove%20problems%2C%20if%20they%20become%20a%20cause%20of%20problems%2C%20their%20use%20must%20be%20stopped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20on%20EVMs%20drew%20a%20response%20from%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader%20must%20resign%20and%20contest%20the%20polls%20again%20if%20he%20does%20not%20trust%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20has%20won%20from%20two%20places.%20The%20same%20EVM%20was%20kept%20there%20also%2C%20so%20he%20should%20say%20that%20the%20EVM%20machine%20was%20faulty%20everywhere%20and%20he%20should%20resign%20and%20contest%20the%20election%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20him%2C%20where%20they%20get%20good%20seats%2C%20the%20EVMs%20are%20fine%2C%20and%20where%20they%20get%20fewer%20seats%2C%20the%20EVMs%20are%20faulty.%20Will%20this%20happen%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20whose%20mutiny%20against%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20split%20the%20party%20and%20toppled%20the%20Sena-NCP-Congress%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20questioned%20the%20Opposition's%20stance%20on%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWherever%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20has%20won%2C%20there%20the%20EVM%20machine%20has%20functioned%20correctly.%20But%20wherever%20they%20lose%2C%20they%20are%20(opposition)%20raising%20objections%20on%20the%20machine.%20What%20kind%20of%20behaviour%20is%20this%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718605860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fmdo3ggr8_uddhav-thackeray-eknath-shinde_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-uddhav-thackeray-2024-lok-sabha-election-result-team-thackeray-vs-shinde-sena-amid-evm-row-on-seat-india-lost-by-48-votes-5906606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20row%20over%20news%20reports%20claiming%20that%20the%20phone%20of%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20candidate's%20aide%20was%20connected%20to%20an%20EVM%20during%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20Mumbai's%20North%20West%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20leaders%20of%20NDA%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20trading%20barbs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-uddhav-thackeray-2024-lok-sabha-election-result-team-thackeray-vs-shinde-sena-amid-evm-row-on-seat-india-lost-by-48-votes-5906606%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.