diatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111052319.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Entertainment%20Weekly%2C%20Madsen%20discussed%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20Cressida's%20fate.%20In%20the%20episodes%20that%20aired%2C%20Cressida%20is%20shown%20leaving%20in%20a%20carriage%2C%20banished%20to%20live%20with%20her%20spinster%20aunt%20in%20Wales.%20However%2C%20Madsen%20revealed%20that%20an%20alternative%20ending%20was%20filmed%20in%20which%20her%20mother%2C%20Lady%20Cowper%2C%20joins%20her%20in%20the%20carriage.%20This%20would%20have%20suggested%20a%20different%20future%20for%20Cressida%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fbridgerton-season-3-alternate-ending-for-cressida-cowper-revealed%2Farticleshow%2F111052319.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Twin%20Meetings%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Takes%20Stock%20Of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Situation%2C%20Amarnath%20Prep%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20show%20that%20terrorism%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20shrink%20to%20a%20proxy%20war%20from%20highly%20organised%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20at%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation.%20The%20minister%20said%20the%20fight%20against%20terror%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20is%20in%20its%20decisive%20phase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sunday's%20meeting%20at%20the%20North%20Block%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20Army%20Chief%20Manoj%20Pande%20among%20others%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20also%20directed%20security%20agencies%20to%20replicate%20the%20successes%20achieved%20in%20Kashmir%20valley%20through%20the%20area%20domination%20and%20the%20Zero%20Terror%20Plan%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20attacks%2C%20in%20which%20nine%20pilgrims%20and%20a%20CRPF%20personnel%20were%20killed%2C%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Jammu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20terrorism%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20asserted%20that%20the%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20will%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20rooting%20out%20terrorism%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20home%20minister%20directed%20security%20agencies%20to%20work%20in%20mission%20mode%20and%20ensure%20quick%20response%20in%20a%20coordinated%20manner%20while%20identifying%20vulnerable%20areas%20and%20addressing%20security%20concerns%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20the%20changes%20that%20have%20come%20about%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20have%20yielded%20positive%20results%20with%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20terror-related%20incidents%20and%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20record%20flow%20of%20tourists%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20appreciated%20the%20role%20of%20the%20security%20agencies%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20for%20the%20successful%20conduct%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20witnessed%20a%20record%20voter%20turnout%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20home%20minister%20was%20given%20a%20thorough%20briefing%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20well%20as%20the%20places%20where%20security%20forces%20plan%20to%20intensify%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%20meeting%20came%20three%20days%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20held%20a%20similar%20stock-taking%20exercise%20and%20directed%20officials%20to%20deploy%20the%20%26quot%3Bfull%20spectrum%20of%20counter-terror%20capabilities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerror%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerrorists%20struck%20four%20places%20in%20the%20Reasi%2C%20Kathua%20and%20Doda%20districts%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20as%20many%20days%20last%20week%2C%20killing%20nine%20pilgrims%20headed%20to%20a%20temple%20as%20well%20as%20a%20CRPF%20personnel.%20Seven%20security%20personnel%20and%20several%20others%20were%20injured.%20Two%20suspected%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20were%20also%20killed%20in%20an%20encounter%20in%20Kathua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%209%2C%20terrorists%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%2053-seater%20bus%20carrying%20pilgrims%20when%20it%20was%20en%20route%20to%20the%20Mata%20Vaishno%20Devi%20shrine%20in%20Katra%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Khori%20temple.%20The%20bus%2C%20which%20had%20pilgrims%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Delhi%2C%20plunged%20into%20a%20gorge%2C%20killing%20nine%20people%20and%20injuring%2041%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2011%2C%20terrorists%20fired%20at%20a%20joint%20checkpost%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20and%20police%20at%20Chattergalla%20in%20Bhaderwah%20while%20a%20search%20party%20in%20the%20Gandoh%20area%20of%20Doda%20district%20was%20attacked%20the%20next%20day%2C%20resulting%20in%20injuries%20to%20seven%20security%20personnel%2C%20including%20a%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20For%20Amarnath%20Yatra%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20meeting%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20reviewed%20the%20preparations%20for%20the%20annual%20Amarnath%20pilgrimage%20and%20said%20the%20government's%20priority%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20conduct%20of%20the%20yatra%20so%20that%20pilgrims%20don't%20face%20any%20difficulties.%20The%20yatra%20begins%20on%20June%2029%20and%20Mr%20Shah%20instructed%20to%20ensure%20sufficient%20deployment%20of%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensure%20a%20convenient%20and%20hassle-free%20experience%20for%20devotees%20and%20adopt%20eco-friendly%20measures%20in%20management%20of%20the%20Amarnath%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%204.5%20lakh%20devotees%20visited%20the%20cave%20shrine%20last%20year.%20The%20pilgrims%20travel%20through%20two%20routes%2C%20Baltal%20and%20Pahalgam%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718605560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ff4mcsn2_amit-shah-doval-jammu-and-kashmir-meeting_625x300_17_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-jammu-and-kashmir-in-twin-meetings-amit-shah-takes-stock-of-j-k-situation-amarnath-prep-5907226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20show%20that%20terrorism%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20shrink%20to%20a%20proxy%20war%20from%20highly%20organised%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-jammu-and-kashmir-in-twin-meetings-amit-shah-takes-stock-of-j-k-situation-amarnath-prep-5907226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-jammu-and-kashmir-in-twin-meetings-amit-shah-takes-stock-of-j-k-situation-amarnath-prep-5907226%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-jammu-and-kashmir-in-twin-meetings-amit-shah-takes-stock-of-j-k-situation-amarnath-prep-5907226%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Makes%20Task%20Of%20Secutity%20Forces%20Difficult%20In%20Latest%20J%26amp%3BK%20Terror%20Attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20of%20unease%20hangs%20in%20the%20air%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Poonch%2C%20even%20at%20a%20bustling%20marketplace.%20The%20mountains%20overlooking%20the%20border%20town%20are%20hiding%20a%20troubling%20reality%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20--%20highly%20trained%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20holed%20up%20in%20the%20green%20forest%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20army%20has%20intensified%20patrolling%20after%20the%20recent%20spike%20in%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20searching%20these%20dense%20forests%20is%20a%20challenging%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20gap%20of%2018%20years%2C%20terrorism%20has%20resurfaced%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri.%20The%20first%20major%20attack%20on%20the%20army%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Surankote%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20troubling%20reality%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20mountains%20has%20upset%20all%20security%20calculations%20about%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20situation%20has%20worsened%20after%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20it%20special%20status%20under%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20attacks%2C%20including%20the%20targeting%20of%20pilgrims%20in%20Reasi%2C%20have%20evoked%20a%20strong%20response%20from%20the%20Central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20asked%20security%20forces%20to%20deploy%20their%20full%20spectrum%20of%20anti-terror%20capabilities%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20called%20a%20high-level%20security%20review%20meeting%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Ground%20Zero%2C%20the%20priority%20is%20securing%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Pir%20Panjal%20and%20Chenab%20Valley%20regions.%20It%20is%20these%20areas%20that%20terrorists%20targeted%20and%20massacred%20many%20Hindus%20before%20terrorism%20was%20eliminated%20from%20the%C2%A0%20region%20two%20decades%20ago.%20The%20police%20say%20terrorists%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20situation%20similar%20to%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%2010%20years%2C%20between%201995%20and%202005%2C%20when%20terrorists%20tried%20to%20destabilize%20Jammu%2C%20Rajouri%2C%20Rajouri%2C%20Doda%20and%20Kishtwar%2C%20security%20forces%20with%20the%20help%20people%20completely%20destroyed%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RR%20Swain%2C%20the%C2%A0%20police%20chief%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20enemy%20is%20again%20trying%20to%20pose%20a%20similar%20challenge.%20We%20are%20determined%20to%20give%20them%20a%20fitting%20reply.%20We%20will%20kill%20them%20one%20by%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20revamped%20the%20village%20Defence%20Guards%20%E2%80%93%20village%20residents%20trained%20and%20armed%20by%20the%20government%20--%20sensitising%20them%20about%20the%20current%20situation..%20Most%20of%2028%2C000%20Village%20Defence%20Guards%20in%20Doda%2C%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20regions%20are%20drawn%20from%20the%20Hindu%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20telling%20the%20VDGs%20to%20remain%20alert%20and%20inform%20them%20whenever%20they%20notice%20any%20suspicious%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20a%20successful%20joint%20operation%20by%20the%20army%20and%20police%2C%20with%20the%20unwavering%20support%20of%20locals%2C%20eliminated%20militancy.%20But%20since%202021%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20disturbing%20resurgence.%20The%20deadly%20attacks%20that%20started%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%2C%20have%20now%20spread%20to%20the%20Doda%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayed%20Ahfadul%20Mujtaba%2C%20a%20former%20police%20officer%20who%20led%20the%20operation%20to%20eliminate%20terrorism%20from%20Rajouri%20in%202003%2C%20said%20resurgence%20of%20terror%20in%20the%20region%20can%20be%20defeated%20only%20if%20the%20local%20population%20is%20on%20the%20side%20of%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20police%20officers%2C%20we%20are%20not%20dealing%20with%20territory.%20We%20are%20dealing%20with%20the%20population.%20And%20if%20more%20people%20are%20on%20your%20side%2C%20the%20task%20becomes%20easier.%20There%20was%20a%20need%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20do%20comprehensive%20policing%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20people%20along%20so%20the%20flow%20of%20information%20comes%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shadow%20of%20Terror%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%202021%2C%2039%20soldiers%20and%2020%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20terrorist%20groups%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20Pooch%20and%20Rajouri%20region%20and%20almost%20an%20equal%20number%20in%20and%20around%20Doda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20army%20said%2025-30%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20are%20operating%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri.%20None%20was%20killed%20so%20far%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20in%20the%20area%20appear%20to%20be%20well%20trained%20in%20jungle%20warfare%20and%20are%20using%20state-of-the-art%20weapons%20including%20US-made%20M4%20carbine%20and%20armour%20piercing%20bullets.%C2%A0%20The%20micro-%20satellite%20communication%20system%20which%20is%20hard%20to%20intercept%20has%20also%20made%20it%20to%20their%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20major%20attack%20on%20Special%20Forces%20in%20November%2C%20the%20army%20said%20the%20terrorists%20have%20been%20trained%20in%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan.%20They%20managed%20to%20get%20away%20after%20every%20attack%20except%20on%20November%205%2C%20when%20the%20army%20killed%20the%20two%20terrorists%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%20that%20cost%20the%20lives%20of%20five%20Special%20Forces%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20us%20time%20to%20eliminate%20them%20but%20our%20brave%20soldiers%20killed%20these%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lieutenant%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%2C%20a%20senior%20army%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20fallen%20commandos%20of%20Special%20Forces%20was%20Hawaldar%20Abdul%20Majid.%20His%20family%20%E2%80%93%20residents%20of%20Ajot%20village%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20in%20Poonch%20%E2%80%93%20said%20they%20are%20proud%20of%20his%20sacrifice%20and%20worry%20about%20the%20repeated%20infiltration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20come%20these%20terrorists%20infiltrate%20so%20easily%3F%20Despite%20fencing%20of%20border%20and%20large%20troops%20deployed%2C%20how%20can%20they%20infiltrate%20from%20Pakistan%20frequently%20and%20carry%20out%20attacks%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fazal%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20relative%20of%20fallen%20commando.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20say%20the%20series%20of%20attacks%20on%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Jammu%20region%20indicate%20a%20clear%20intent%20to%20escalate%20the%20situation%20and%20create%20communal%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-border%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20serious%20challenge%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20key%20reason%20of%20the%20resurgence%20of%20terrorism.%20Dealing%20with%20this%20challenge%20could%20prove%20more%20complex%20than%20it%20appears.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718605260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F66dkrj38_jammu-combing-op-pti_625x300_10_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-makes-task-of-secutity-forces-difficult-in-latest-j-k-terror-attacks-5904852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sense%20of%20unease%20hangs%20in%20the%20air%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Poonch%2C%20even%20at%20a%20bustling%20marketplace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-makes-task-of-secutity-forces-difficult-in-latest-j-k-terror-attacks-5904852%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-makes-task