20at%20some%20time%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20if%2C%20it's%20more%20of%20a%20question%20of%20when%20we%20will%20have%20a%20bird%20flu%20pandemic%2C''%20Mr%20Redfield%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20bird%20flu%20has%20a%20''significant%20mortality''%20when%20it%20enters%20humans%20compared%20to%20COVID-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20mortality%20rate%20was%200.6%20per%20cent%20for%20Covid-19%2C%20Mr%20Redfield%20said%20the%20mortality%20for%20the%20bird%20flu%20would%20probably%20be%20''somewhere%20between%2025%20and%2050%20per%20cent.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%C2%A0US%20officials%20reported%20the%20country's%20third%20human%20case%20of%20bird%20flu%20linked%20to%20the%20current%20outbreak%20of%20the%20virus%20in%20dairy%20cattle.%C2%A0Worldwide%2C%20doctors%20have%20detected%2015%20human%20infections%20caused%20by%20bird%20flu%20strain%20H5N1.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20not%20yet%20evidence%20that%20the%20virus%20is%20spreading%20between%20humans%2C%20Mr%20Redfield%20explained%20that%20there%20must%20be%20five%20amino%20acids%20present%20for%20bird%20flu%20to%20gain%20a%20propensity%20to%20bind%20to%20a%20human%20receptor%20''and%20then%20be%20able%20to%20go%20human%20to%20human''%20like%20Covid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Once%20the%20virus%20gains%20the%20ability%20to%20attach%20to%20the%20human%20receptor%20and%20then%20go%20human%20to%20human%2C%20that's%20when%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%2C''%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20unknown%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20for%20the%20five%20amino%20acids%20to%20change%2C%20but%20Mr%20Redfield%20said%20he%20is%20concerned%20because%20it's%20being%20detected%20in%20cattle%20herds%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20know%20exactly%20what%20amino%20acids%20I%20have%20to%20change%20because%20in%202012%2C%20against%20my%20recommendation%2C%20the%20scientists%20that%20did%20these%20experiments%20published%20them.%20So%2C%20the%20recipe%20for%20how%20to%20make%20bird%20flu%20highly%20infectious%20for%20humans%20is%20already%20out%20there%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20highly%20pathogenic%20avian%20influenza%20virus%20has%20spread%20to%20infect%20more%20than%2050%20animal%20species%2C%20including%2C%20from%20March%2C%20dairy%20cattle%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20Europe%2C%20American%20farmers%20are%20allowed%20to%20feed%20cattle%20ground-up%20chicken%20waste%2C%20which%20some%20scientists%20say%20may%20be%20a%20risk%20factor%20for%20bird%20flu%20--%20though%20the%20feed%20industry%20has%20challenged%20this%20claim%20and%20US%20authorities%20believe%20wild%20birds%20are%20responsible%20for%20infecting%20cows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718599920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fus-bird-flu-reuters_650x400_81454053169.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-health-expert-predicts-the-next-pandemic-will-be-from-bird-flu-just-a-matter-of-time-5906608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20mortality%20rate%20was%200.6%20per%20cent%20for%20Covid-19%2C%20Mr%20Redfield%20said%20the%20mortality%20for%20the%20bird%20flu%20would%20probably%20be%20''somewhere%20between%2025%20and%2050%20per%20cent.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-health-expert-predicts-the-next-pandemic-will-be-from-bird-flu-just-a-matter-of-time-5906608%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-health-expert-predicts-the-next-pandemic-will-be-from-bird-flu-just-a-matter-of-time-5906608%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-health-expert-predicts-the-next-pandemic-will-be-from-bird-flu-just-a