C%20a%20close%20family%20friend.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20its%20design%20was%20another%20similar%20building%20prototype%20that%20Gwilliam%20had%20constructed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbloolagoon.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloo%20Lagoon%20Eco%20Village%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20resort%20located%20along%20the%20east%20coast%20of%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66693e0fe07904901817fc59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20for%20a%20road%20trip%20during%20our%20first%20week%20in%20Bali%2C%20and%20we%20stopped%20by%20the%20Bloo%20Lagoon%20Eco%20Village%20because%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20their%20permaculture%20garden.%20In%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20garden%20was%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20our%20house%2C%20and%20we%20just%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20its%20concept%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20six-meter%20cube%20made%20from%20steel%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20incorporating%20that%20material%20into%20their%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20using%20steel%2C%20you%20can%20have%20very%20small%20foundational%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6666b9a0e079049018174a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20couple's%20house%20is%20supported%20by%20six%20steel%20pillars%20and%20made%20from%20local%20brick.%20Because%20it's%20light%2C%20the%20house%20can%20also%20be%20taken%20down%20and%20fit%20in%20a%20container%20to%20be%20moved%20if%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20take%20much%20space%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20require%20many%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20explained%2C%20Gwilliam%20and%20the%20couple%20were%20inspired%20by%20architect%20R.%20Buckminster%20Fuller's%20ideas%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moma.org%2Fcollection%2Fworks%2F804%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522How%2520much%2520does%2520your%2520house%2Cweighed%2520only%2520three%2520tons%253B%2520its%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20weight%20of%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20related%20to%20its%20environmental%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6666b99fed9a404d829c0038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20material%20was%20extracted%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20transported%2C%20and%20transformed%3F%20When%20you%20have%20a%20big%20concrete%20villa%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20those%20is%20colossal%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20home's%20interiors%20are%20fairly%20minimal%2C%20with%20each%20piece%20of%20furniture%20designed%20by%20the%20couple%20and%20made%20by%20local%20craftsmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20we're%20getting%20older%2C%20we're%20less%20attached%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20also%20what%20the%20idea%20of%20coming%20here%20was%20about%2C%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshannen-doherty-90210-declutter-downsize-breast-cancer-mom-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20attached%20to%20material%20things%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20more%20attached%20to%20how%20we%20feel%2C%20how%20we%20live%2C%20how%20we%20are%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20as%20parents%2C%20and%20just%20focusing%20more%20on%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20even%20with%20an%20infant%20son%20in%20tow%2C%20they%20have%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20they%20spend%20time%20as%20a%20family%20and%20walk%20their%20three%20dogs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealong%20the%20beach%2C%20which%20is%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20away%20on%20foot.%20The%20couple%20also%20has%20two%20cats%2C%20and%20they%20rear%20chickens%20and%20grow%20their%20own%20produce%20in%20the%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20little%20play%20area%20for%20the%20baby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66693e23764df1611258c672%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20little%20play%20area%20for%20the%20baby.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20that%20we%20didn't%20think%20about%20when%20we%20were%20creating%20the%20house%20was%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20have%20a%20baby%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20very%20baby-proof%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucie%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20layout%20can%20be%20easily%20adjusted%20because%20of%20the%20house's%20design%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20add%20two%20more%20rooms%2C%20we%20can%20still%20do%20it%20within%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20improve%20it%20as%20we%20grow%20according%20to%20our%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22482b5f10-b856-495e-bee0-8f6d7d8f90de%5C%22%3EBe%20part%20of%20the%20solution%2C%20not%20the%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETanguy%20acknowledges%20that%20mass%20tourism%20has%20greatly%20impacted%20Bali%20and%20its%20natural%20ecosystems.%20He%20points%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalobserver.com%2F2024%2F04%2F29%2Fnews%2Ftipping-point-tourism-sustainability-bali-water-shortages%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOver%252065%2520per%2520cent%2520of%2Cwater%2520in%2520a%2520few%2520years.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eisland's%20ongoing%20water%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20Bali's%20natural%20landscapes%20for%20materials%20as%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66693e2ee07904901817fc60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20garden.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20should%20move%20here%20if%20they%20want%20to%20contribute%2C%20but%20if%20they%20are%20here%20to%20just%20extract%20value%20from%20the%20people%2C%20from%20unregulated%20resource%20management%2C%20then%20they%20should%20reconsider%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20fragile%20part%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20eco-tourism%20alternatives%20that%20are%20now%20available%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20hotels%20that%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20better%2C%20who%20are%20growing%20their%20own%20food%2C%20doing%20wastewater%20treatment%20or%20sourcing%20their%20food%20locally%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20come%20to%20Bali%2C%20go%20there%20and%20support.%20The%20same%20thing%20for%20restaurants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20built%20or%20renovated%20your%20dream%20home%3F%20If%20you've%20got%20a%20story%20to%20share%2C%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20me%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aagoh%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eagoh%40businessi