th%20IBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McDonald's%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20the%20decision%20to%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%20customers%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20technology%20in%202021%20when%20McDonald's%20entered%20a%20global%20partnership%20with%20IBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20Drive%20Thru%20Menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666f05c4ed9a404d829e2f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcDonald's%20drive-thru%20menu.%20%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20partnership%2C%20IBM%20acquired%20McD%20Tech%20Labs%2C%20which%20McDonald's%20created%20after%20taking%20control%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-buys-ai-speech-company-apprente-automate-drive-thrus-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20speech%20company%20Apprente%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20companies%20developed%20and%20deployed%20the%20technology%20during%20the%20test%20period%20to%20%26quot%3Bdetermine%20if%20an%20automated%20voice%20ordering%20solution%20could%20simplify%20operations%20for%20crew%20and%20create%20a%20faster%2C%20improved%20experience%20for%20our%20fans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-drive-thrus-voice-recognition-automated-chicago-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20CEO%20Chris%20Kempczinski%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20CNBC%20in%20June%202021%20that%20voice%20recognition%20technology%20was%20accurate%20about%2085%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20but%20human%20staff%20had%20to%20assist%20with%20about%20one%20in%20five%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20failures%2C%20however%2C%20went%20viral%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20of%20drive-thru%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok