pite%20trying%20his%20level%20best%20to%20conform%20to%20the%20standards%20set%20by%20society%20and%20his%20parents%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20live%20a%20lie.%20At%20his%20lowest%2C%20he%20tried%20taking%20his%20own%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20ending%20my%20life%20to%20avoid%20bringing%20shame%20to%20the%20family.%20It%20took%20me%2048%20pills%20to%20understand%20that%20I%20too%20am%20important%20in%20this%20world.%20Dying%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20helped%20me%20understand%20about%20living.%20I%20too%20deserved%20to%20live%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-500x702.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20with%20their%20son%20and%20two%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-500x702.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-214x300.jpeg%20214w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-768x1078.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-1094x1536.jpeg%201094w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177-150x211.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri1-1718194177.jpeg%201118w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20with%20their%20son%20and%20two%20dogs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20chose%20himself%20and%20his%20mental%20health%20over%20conforming%20to%20his%20parent%E2%80%99s%20wishes%2C%20Srivatsan%20moved%20to%20Singapore%20when%20he%20was%20