nd%20after%20moving%20to%20refugee%20camps%20in%20Asansol%2C%20Serampore%20and%20Canning%2C%20we%20were%20settled%20here%20by%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Dr%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Ray%20in%201957%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Biswas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20family%20was%20given%20a%20land%20measuring%20nine%20%3Cem%3Ebighas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20as%20families%20grew%2C%20the%20plots%20were%20divided%20and%20distributed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2046-year-old%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20digging%20to%20plant%20the%20saplings.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-digging-land_11zon-1717770332-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWomen%20digging%20to%20plant%20the%20saplings.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Biswas%20began%20planting%20mangrove%20saplings%20along%20Bidyadhari%20river%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20children%20in%202005%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20homemakers%2C%20disabled%20people%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98tiger%20widows%E2%80%99%20(women%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%20to%20tiger%20attacks)%20joined%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20over%20the%20years%2C%20this%20band%20of%20people%20became%20the%20JSB%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20include%20more%20than%20200%20homemakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20Sundari%20which%20is%20dominant%20here%20and%20provides%20critical%20habitat%20and%20resources%20for%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20flora%20and%20fauna%2C%20including%20serving%20as%20a%20nursery%20ground%20for%20many%20aquatic%20species.%20Its%20leaves%20have%20glands%20that%20can%20excrete%20excess%20salt%2C%20allowing%20the%20tree%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20saline%20environment%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nivash%20Golder%20(36)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Jharkhali%2C%20Ashrampada%2C%20who%20heads%20a%20group%20of%2050%20women%20of%20the%20JSB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterestingly%2C%20it%20is%20adapted%20to%20thrive%20in%20freshwater%20environments%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20dominate%20areas%20with%20lower%20salinity%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWmen-preparing-land_11zon-1717770425.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20plantation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWmen-preparing-land_11zon-1717770425.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWmen-preparing-land_11zon-1717770425-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWmen-preparing-land_11zon-1717770425-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWmen-preparing-land_11zon-1717770425-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co