rs%E2%80%99%2017th%20Century%20Haveli%20Offers%20200-YO%20Recipes%2C%20Jawai%20Leopard%20Trails%20%26amp%3B%20Village%20Walks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20one%20of%20the%20stories%20my%20imagination%20would%20create%20was%20one%20where%20I%20would%20become%20a%20princess.%20While%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20European%20princesses%20in%20their%20beautiful%20gowns%2C%20there%20was%20something%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20Indian%20princess%20that%20always%20made%20me%20want%20to%20be%20like%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dazzling%20dresses%2C%20the%20grand%20palaces%2C%20and%20the%20luxurious%20lifestyle%20always%20attracted%20me.%20On%20a%20trip%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20touching%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F188515%2Fheritage-building-restoration-woman-award-winning-architect-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalls%20of%20palaces%20and%20havelis%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20imagining%20what%20it%20would%20have%20been%20like%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20royals%20living%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20this%20was%20a%20childhood%20dream%2C%20and%20while%20it%20might%20seem%20fanciful%20to%20many%2C%20you%20can%20actually%20experience%20this%20dream%20by%20staying%20in%20a%2017th-century%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%20%3C%2Fem%3E(palace)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERawla%20Bisalpur%2C%20a%20boutique%20homestay%20located%20near%20the%20Jawai%20Bandh%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F184890%2Fdelhi-hero-reforests-aravalli-biodiversity-park-native-trees-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20Aravalli%20Range%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealmost%20halfway%20between%20Udaipur%20and%20Jodhpur%2C%20is%20the%20royal%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20your%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20our%20walls%20coul