%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhushboo%20has%20repurposed%20agro-waste%20to%20find%20alternatives%20for%20single-use%20plastic.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20she%20started%20her%20professional%20career%2C%20she%20often%20wondered%20about%20various%20ways%20to%20live%20sustainably%20and%20create%20a%20larger%20impact%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20trekking%20tour%20in%20Ladakh%20in%202015%2C%20Khushboo%20shares%20that%20she%20found%20plastic%20waste%20even%20in%20the%20remotest%20of%20all%20places%20there.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20leftover%20plastic%20like%20sachets%20being%20burned%20near%20a%20water%20stream.%20It%20really%20hit%20me%20how%20deep-rooted%20the%20problem%20had%20become.%20This%20needed%20to%20be%20solved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20in%202018%2C%20she%20went%20to%20pursue%20her%20masters%20in%20material%20development%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain%2C%20to%20formally%20educate%20herself%20in%20circular%20economy%20and%20design%20thinking.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20actually%20build%20materials%20that%20can%20replace%20plastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20spent%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Khushboo%20formally%20launched%20her%20company%20in%202021%20along%20with%20her%20brother%20Ronak%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Chanakya%20Medh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInk%20from%20seaweed%2C%20bubble%20wrap%20from%20coir%20%26amp%3B%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShedding%20light%20on%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20packaging%20industry%2C%20Khushboo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20multiple%20types%20of%20plastic%20used%20for%20different%20applications.%20For%20example%2C%20ink%20printed%20on%20the%20packaging%20is%20toxic%20as%20well%2C%20and%20contains%20heavy%20metal%20additives%2C%20synthetic%20chemicals%2C%20and%20paraffin%20waxes.%20So%20even%20if%20you%20have%20a%20compostable%20material%2C%20you%20have%20to%20print%20on%20it%C2%A0%20with%20regular%2C%20toxic%20ink.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20people%20fail%20to%20notice%20layers%20of%20plastic%20lamination%20on%20packaging%20and%20the%20synthetic%20glue%20used%20in%20the%20sticker%20industry.%20These%20are%20the%20areas%20we%20strived%20to%20work%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20material%20innovation%20company%2C%20Khushboo%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20solve%20industrial%20problems%20using%20natural%20materials%20which%20can%20be%20composted%20at%20home.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20innovated%20a%20coating%20compostable%20at%20home%20which%20naturally%20makes%20paper%20water-resistant%20and%20heat-fillable%20%E2%80%94%20two%20main%20properties%20that%20plastic%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20uses%20natural%20pigments%20and%20seaweed%20to%20make%20eco-friendly%20inks.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-3-1717687943-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352336%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20uses%20natural%20pigments%20and%20seaweed%20to%20make%20eco-friendly%20inks.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20utilised%20heavy%20coconut%20coir%20that%20are%20usually%20used%20to%20make%20mattresses%2C%20rugs%2C%20or%20doormats.%20This%20offers%20excellent%20cushioning%20properties%20for%20fragile%20products%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20direct%20replacement%20for%20bubble%20wrap.%20We%20also%20use%20tamarind%20seeds%20to%20make%20water-based%20glue%20and%20are%20replacing%20the%20toxic%20ink%20with%20our%20eco-friendly%20ink%20that%20has%20been%20developed%20from%20seaweed%20and%20natural%20pigments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20why%20she%20zeroed%20down%20on%20using%20seaweed%2C%20Khushboo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSeaweed%20has%20a%20polymer%20structure%20and%20behaves%20very%20similar%20to%20plastic%20in%20terms%20of%20stretchability%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20transparency.%20It%20can%20go%20back%20to%20the%20planet%20much%20more%20easily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20materials%20allow%20everything%20that%20is%20on%20the%20package%20and%20inside%20the%20package%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20biodegradable.%20and%20compostable%20at%20home.%20So%2C%20tomorrow%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20done%20using%20the%20product%2C%20you%20can%20dump%20it%20in%20your%20backyard%20and%20it%20will%20compost%20within%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Khushoo%20says%2C%20the%20price%20difference%20is%20also%20at%20par%20with%20only%20a%2010%20percent%20difference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20market%2C%20a%20250g%20paper%20pillow%20pouch%20with%20a%20plastic%20lamination%20(the%20pouches%20in%20which%20items%20like%20milk%2C%20chips%2C%20spices%20are%20sold%20in)%20costs%20Rs%207%20whereas%20our%20natural%20pouch%20costs%20between%20Rs%207.5%20to%208.%20We%20made%20our%20products%20affordable%20and%20compatible%20so%20that%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20for%20more%20and%20more%20people%20to%20switch%20to%20natural%20materials%20instead%20of%20plastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khushboo's%20startup%20has%20innovated%20eco-friendly%20coating%20which%20replaces%20the%20laminated%20paper.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhushboo%E2%80%99s%20startup%20has%20innovated%20eco-friendly%20coating%20which%20replaces%20the%20laminated%20paper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20products%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20are%20equally%20durable.%20We%20do%20not%20require%20any%20tape%20or%20synthetic%20glue%20and%20our%20packaging%20products%20keep%20your%20flowers%2C%20powder%2C%20liquid%20detergent%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20takeaway%20food%20items%20safe.%20The%20biggest%20advantage%20is%20that%20you%20are%20not%20compromising%20on%20any%20of%20the%20uses%20while%20also%20cont